Dependencies:
* zsh (as late as possible; >4.3.10 misses a lot of features)
* vim (latest and greatest with python support)
* tmux (latest and greatest for best results)

Good things happens:
* pyflakes (easy_install pyflakes)

To install:
`curl etc.ninjaloot.se | zsh -s - n1ck3`

Then, to update at any time:
Just run `update` at the command line.
